pokedexEntries.red: Always furious and tenacious to boot. It will not abandon chasing its quarry until it is caught.
pokedexEntries.blue: Always furious and tenacious to boot. It will not abandon chasing its quarry until it is caught.
pokedexEntries.yellow: It stops being angry only when nobody else is around. To view this moment is very difficult.
pokedexEntries.gold: If approached while asleep, it may awaken and angrily give chase in a groggy state of semi-sleep.
pokedexEntries.silver: It becomes wildly furious if it even senses someone looking at it. It chases anyone that meets its glare.
pokedexEntries.crystal: It will beat up anyone who makes it mad, even if it has to chase them until the end of the world.
pokedexEntries.ruby: When Primeape becomes furious, its blood circulation is boosted. In turn, its muscles are made even stronger. However, it also becomes much less intelligent at the same time.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: When Primeape becomes furious, its blood circulation is boosted. In turn, its muscles are made even stronger. However, it also becomes much less intelligent at the same time.
pokedexEntries.emerald: When it becomes furious, its blood circulation becomes more robust, and its muscles are made stronger. But it also becomes much less intelligent.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: It is always outrageously furious. If it gives chase, it will tenaciously track the target no matter how far.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: Always furious and tenacious to boot. It will not abandon chasing its quarry until it catches up.
pokedexEntries.diamond: It grows angry if you see its eyes and gets angrier if you run. If you beat it, it gets even madder.
pokedexEntries.pearl: It grows angry if you see its eyes and gets angrier if you run. If you beat it, it gets even madder.

pokedexEntries.omegaRuby: When Primeape becomes furious, its blood circulation is boosted. In turn, its muscles are made even stronger. However, it also becomes much less intelligent at the same time.
pokedexEntries.alphaSapphire: When Primeape becomes furious, its blood circulation is boosted. In turn, its muscles are made even stronger. However, it also becomes much less intelligent at the same time.
pokedexEntries.sun: It has been known to become so angry that it dies as a result. Its face looks peaceful in death, however.
pokedexEntries.moon: Some researchers theorize that Primeape remains angry even when inside a Poké Ball.
pokedexEntries.ultraSun: It will never forgive opponents who have angered it. Even after it has beaten them down until they can’t move, it never ever forgives.
pokedexEntries.ultraMoon: The blood vessels in its brain are sturdier than those of other Pokémon, so it can stay healthy despite its constant raging.
